examples.en: Has anybody asked for me?
He asked to speak.
He asked me a favour.
He asked her to dance.
I asked for a hot drink.
She asked me politely for the book.
examples.ru: Она вежливо попросила у меня книгу.

examples.en: I asked her to marry me.
examples.ru: Я попросил ее выйти за меня замуж.

examples.en: He asked it of me.
Prices asked are very wide.
My mother asked after you.
examples.ru: Моя мама спрашивала, как вы себя чувствуете.

examples.en: She asked him for a loan.
examples.ru: Она попросила у него денег взаймы.

examples.en: Has he asked you out yet?
examples.ru: Он тебя уже пригласил на свидание?

examples.en: He asked me about my work.
I asked him where he lived.
examples.ru: Я спросил его, где он живёт.

examples.en: We asked how we could help.
examples.ru: Мы спросили, каким образом мы могли бы помочь.

examples.en: I asked them to keep quiet.
He asked to open the window.
I asked the man at reception.
examples.ru: Я спросил мужчину у стойки администрации.

examples.en: He asked for a drink of water.
'What's your name?' she asked.
Karen asked to see the doctor.
They asked us, nay, begged us.
She asked for political asylum.
He asked if his wife was there.
examples.ru: Он спросил, там ли его жена.

examples.en: We asked her for her autograph.
The guest asked for the manager.
Brashly, she asked for a rebate.
I asked for a 6 o'clock wake-up.
examples.ru: Я попросил, чтобы меня разбудили в шесть.

examples.en: The professor asked for silence.
'Are you lost?' the driver asked.
